|available_on_android_as_well = Yes.}}'''Morocco''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in October 2019. Its default cities are Casablanca,  Fez, Marrakesh and Tangier. The capital, Rabat, is strangely absent.

Morocco was added as a new country to BitLife in late October 2019 during the Haunted Update, as the only non-Haunted addition to the game. [[Czech Republic]], [[Ecuador]], [[Hong Kong]], [[Malaysia]], [[Monaco]], [[Pakistan]], and [[Syria]] were also added at the same time.

